# OpenCode AI Assistant Ignore File
# Tells OpenCode which files/directories to skip when searching or reading

# ========== Build Outputs ==========
**/target/
**/bin/
**/build/

# ========== IDE ==========
**/.idea/
**/*.iml
**/*.ipr
**/*.iws
**/.settings/
**/.classpath
**/.project

# ========== Dependencies ==========
**/.mvn/
**/node_modules/
**/.gradle/

# ========== Version Control ==========
**/.git/

# ========== Logs ==========
**/*.log

# ========== Framework-generated (not project code) ==========
sql/

# ========== Generated/Temporary ==========
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/*.xml.versionsBackup
**/rebel.xml
